{"title":"匈牙利的春天","authors":["孙用"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"匈牙利的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这伟大的自由节日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我记起了她的十五年："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年前的艰难缔造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年来的奋斗、发展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她刚跨进了六十年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新生的事物动地惊天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匈牙利的春天又到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要高唱欢乐的诗篇："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多瑙河畔百鸟喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绮丽春色满车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革新花竞放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竞赛红旗映蓝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄人物数今朝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助协作把战挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人争夸“劳动队”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义风格高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜春风到农家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千村万户合作化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义前程好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最红还是“集体”花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里田野遍春光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处春耕春播忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担起太阳赶星月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取丰收多打粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是匈牙利的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好的生活光辉灿烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又站在多瑙河边了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到了欢乐的呼喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在六十年代的第一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放十五周年这一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要和她的人民一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同声高唱歌颂的诗篇！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}